article.description: — Nick Stampley and Zay Williams scored 17 points apiece as Troy beat Division II-member Spring Hill 90-73 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Stampley, Williams carry Troy over D-II Spring Hill 90-73
article.linkText: Stampley, Williams carry Troy over D-II Spring Hill 90-73
article.story: TROY, Ala. -- — Nick Stampley and Zay Williams scored 17 points apiece as Troy beat Division II-member Spring Hill 90-73 on Tuesday night. Desmond Williams added 15 points with a career-high 15 rebounds for the Trojans. Jaden Gray had 19 points for the Badgers, Beril Kabamba scored 13 with seven rebounds and Christian Brandt scored 10. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
